  "code": "%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': { 'primaryColor': '#10b981'}}}%%\nsequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n    participant R as 🖼️ Renderer<br/>(renderer.js)\n    participant P as 📡 Preload<br/>(preload.js)\n    participant M as 🖥️ Main<br/>(index.js)\n    participant S as ⚙️ Services\n    participant MCP as 🤖 MCP Servers\n    participant LM as 🧠 LM Studio\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Application Initialization\n    \n    R->>P: DOMContentLoaded\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke('get-version')\n    M-->>P: { version: '2.0.6' }\n    P-->>R: version\n    \n    R->>P: Initialize LM Studio\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke('lm-studio-connect', url)\n    M->>S: lmStudioClient.connect(url)\n    S->>LM: HTTP GET /v1/models\n    LM-->>S: { models: [...] }\n    S-->>M: { connected: true, models }\n    M-->>P: status\n    P-->>R: Update UI\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Chat Message Flow\n    \n    R->>P: User sends chat message\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke('chatbot-message', msg)\n    M->>S: chatbotService.processMessage(msg)\n    \n    alt Intent: Knowledge Query\n        S->>MCP: evony_search(query)\n        MCP-->>S: { results: [...] }\n    else Intent: Calculation\n        S->>MCP: calc_training(params)\n        MCP-->>S: { result: {...} }\n    else Intent: Protocol\n        S->>MCP: protocol_lookup(id)\n        MCP-->>S: { action: {...} }\n    end\n    \n    S->>S: Build context from MCP results\n    S->>LM: POST /v1/chat/completions\n    LM-->>S: { response: '...' }\n    S-->>M: formatted response\n    M-->>P: response\n    P-->>R: Display in chat\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Traffic Capture Flow\n    \n    R->>P: Webview traffic detected\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.send('traffic-captured', packet)\n    M->>S: proxyMonitor.processPacket(packet)\n    S->>S: Decode AMF3\n    S->>S: Identify action\n    S->>S: Update game state\n    M->>P: mainWindow.webContents.send('traffic-update', entry)\n    P->>R: Update traffic list\n    \n    Note over R,LM: Settings Flow\n    \n    R->>P: User saves settings\n    P->>M: ipcRenderer.invoke('save-settings', settings)\n    M->>S: store.set(settings)\n    M->>S: lmStudioClient.updateSettings(settings.lmStudio)\n    S->>LM: Reconnect if URL changed\n    M-->>P: { success: true }\n    P-->>R: Show confirmation\n",
